{"type": "article", "id": 9450, "title": "Max Mara 限量版 Whitney 手袋", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-12T07:10:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235337FnaYG1skSXJV9Hpc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t最近，美国 Whitney 艺术博物馆正式向公众开放，而 Max Mara 是开幕式的 Party 赞助商。于是我们看到了这款由 Renzo Piano 为 Max Mara 设计的限量版 Whitney 手袋。这款手袋的设计灵感即来自这间博物馆，外形上和博物馆相似，而细纹和金属的使用也和建筑物相呼应。Renzo Piano 一如既往地别出心裁，选用了红色的内衬，和外面如水温柔的颜色形成对比。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052353335DL9ElkW0qV2Tg6C.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235334YB7MCvlFVNWum2EU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.99786325\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235335TL8j9fSOazZGhCHX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235335AZP5czIql4T13NH7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235335GwXy9pnJzW8xud2f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.31837607\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235336B7kVX5H4qeQRWDMv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.31837607\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052353367EMpT9hrq0GIdXg4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.31837607\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235337E1dV3OU4tHqoABXv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.31837607\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}